Class Child

java.lang.Object
Ticket
Child
public class Child
extends Ticket
The class designed to get the ticket price sales for a child ticket and will extend the super class and calculates the sales of the individual child ticket depending on the time of day, the format and after 6 pm or before 6 pm military time format. A child can only attend G and PG movies.
Author:
Herman Mann
